{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_012DWrgQt8Uo78uvA4yxvUQr","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect. Here's your concise reference for peek admin user-detail expansion queries:\n\n---\n\n## DB Schema Reference for Peek Admin User-Detail Expansion\n\n### 1. **linked_accounts** (015)\n- `id` (BIGINT) | `user_id` (TEXT) | `provider` (TEXT) | `provider_account_id` (TEXT) | `status` (TEXT) | `metadata_json` (JSONB) | `linked_at`, `created_at`, `updated_at` (TIMESTAMPTZ)\n- **WHERE clause**: `user_id`\n\n### 2. **telegram_link_tokens** (014)\n- `id` (BIGINT) | `user_id` (TEXT) | `token` (TEXT) | `status` (TEXT) | `telegram_user_id` (TEXT) | `telegram_username` (TEXT) | `expires_at`, `redeemed_at`, `created_at` (TIMESTAMPTZ)\n- **WHERE clause**: `user_id` or `telegram_user_id`\n\n### 3. **Referral tables** (010)\n- **referral_codes**: `id`, `user_id` (PRIMARY/UNIQUE), `wallet`, `code`, `created_at`, `updated_at`\n- **referral_links**: `id`, `referrer_user_id`, `referee_user_id` (UNIQUE), wallets, `created_at`\n- **referral_earnings**: `id`, `referrer_user_id`, `referee_user_id`, wallets, `round_id`, game_type, amounts (BIGINT), rates (INTEGER), `created_at`\n- **referral_claims**: `id` (UUID), `user_id`, `wallet`, `amount_lamports` (BIGINT), `status`, `tx_signature`, `requested_at`, `processed_at`\n- **referral_kol_rates**: `user_id` (PRIMARY), `wallet`, `rate_bps` (INTEGER), `set_by`, `created_at`, `updated_at`\n- **WHERE clauses**: `user_id` (referrer/referee/claimant)\n\n### 4. **Challenge engine tables** (011)\n- **player_points**: `user_id` (PRIMARY), `wallet`, `balance`, `lifetime_earned` (BIGINT), `updated_at`\n- **point_grants**: `id`, `user_id`, `wallet`, `source_type`, `source_id`, `amount` (BIGINT), `metadata` (JSONB), `created_at`\n- **crate_drops**: `id`, `user_id`, `trigger_type`, `trigger_id`, `crate_type`, `contents_amount` (TEXT), `status`, `created_at`, `granted_at`\n- **challenge_assignments**: `id`, `user_id`, `challenge_id` (BIGINT FK), `period_key`, `status`, `progress`, `target` (INT), `assigned_at`, `expires_at`, `completed_at`\n- **WHERE clauses**: `user_id`\n\n### 5. **game_entries** (007)\n- `id` (BIGINT) | `user_id` (TEXT) | `wallet`, `game`, `round_pda`, `match_id` (TEXT) | `amount_lamports`, `payout_lamports` (BIGINT) | `side` (TEXT) | `is_winner` (BOOLEAN) | `created_at`, `settled_at` (TIMESTAMPTZ)\n- **WHERE clause**: `user_id`\n\n### 6. **transactions** (008)\n- `id` (BIGINT) | `user_id` (TEXT, nullable) | `wallet`, `game`, `match_id` (TEXT) | `tx_type` (deposit/payout/refund) | `amount_lamports` (BIGINT) | `tx_sig` (TEXT) | `created_at` (TIMESTAMPTZ)\n- **WHERE clause**: `user_id`\n\n### 7. **fraud_flags** (011)\n- `id` (BIGINT) | `user_id` (TEXT) | `flag_type`, `details` (JSONB), `related_id` (TEXT) | `status` | `created_at`, `resolved_at` (TIMESTAMPTZ)\n- **WHERE clause**: `user_id`\n\n### 8. **event_queue** (009)\n- `id` (BIGINT) | `event_type`, `payload` (JSONB) | `status` | `attempts`, `max_attempts` (INT) | `scheduled_at`, `started_at`, `completed_at` (TIMESTAMPTZ) | `error` (TEXT)\n- **Note**: No direct user_id; lookup via payload or join on related tables\n\n---\n\nAll timestamps are TIMESTAMPTZ. Amounts in lamports (BIGINT). Status/type columns use TEXT with CHECK constraints. Use `user_id` (TEXT) as primary join key for all user-scoped queries."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a7a6576f-78d4-407f-81cd-207cf72e4e2a","uuid":"bc678e95-5a03-408b-869b-dc4ff0acfeec","timestamp":"2026-04-25T11:49:35.779Z","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"I need a quick reference on the schemas of certain backend DB tables for a peek admin user-detail expansion. Look at /workspaces/rng-utopia/backend/migrations/*.sql and report ŌĆö concisely ŌĆö the columns (just names + types) and any user-id-style columns that would be used in the WHERE clauses of:\n\n1. linked_accounts (file 015)\n2. telegram_link_tokens (file 014) \n3. re